                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-70-victim654 t18220417-70-viclabel350"></join> of the ship Truro. On the 5th of April, at night, I saw my things in my chest, in the cabin; the ship lay off <placeName id="t18220417-70-crimeloc351">Wapping</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220417-70-crimeloc351" type="placeName" value="Wapping"></interp>
