                     <interp inst="t18220417-70-person656" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I belong to the ship, I went in pursuit of the thief, and found the prisoner beyond the London Docks, about eight in the morning, with the pantaloons on, and a coat tied in a handkerchief. I gave him in charge.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-70-person657">
                  WILLIAM 
                  GIBBS
               <interp inst="t18220417-70-person657" type="surname" value="GIBBS"></interp>
